Hello Chief Delphi,

Our CAD mentor, Keith, has spent a lot of hours putting together a workshop to teach Fusion 360. Originally, he delivered the workshop in person but has re-recorded it with the aim of making it easier to follow.

Taken from the video’s description:
"Designed for beginner - intermediate skill levels, with an uninterrupted workflow at the end if you prefer to learn that way!

The scope of this is limited to my own knowledge, criticism and feedback is welcome!"

Learn Fusion 360 for FRC
